08eb0a91638a8fe4a016dd548135946129f2a54e.commit.message:
Clean up provider lifecycle and logging:

- Moved lifecycle management methods from FileProvider, FileSystem, and
  FileReplicator to new VfsComponent super-interface.

- Added VfsComponent.setLogger() to allow a logger to be supplied to a
  component.  Still uses Commons-Logging's Log interface.

- Added DefaultFileSystemManager.setLogger(), sets the logger to be supplied
  to the components that are added to the manager.  Defaults to the logger
  provided by LogFactory.getLog().

74a95590af0cc2a5cfb5c62da6e9140dae478fef.commit.message:
File Replicator changes:

- Split PrivilegedFileReplicator out of DefaultFileReplicator.

- DefaultFileReplicator deletes temporary files on exit.

- Replicators are now supplied a FileSystemProviderContext, rather than a
  reference to a DefaultFileSystemManager.

- Can supply a replicator to DefaultFileSystemManager.
